BEFORE BC:

• Registered seven goals and eight assists in 28 games in 2020-21 with the Junior Bruins

• Played two seasons at Dexter Southfield School and was an assistant captain during the 2019-20 season

• Posted 51 points in 30 games during his final year at Dexter

• Skated for one year at Natick High School and two years at Catholic Memorial
